text: Kommunar () is a rural locality (a village) in Kaltovsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 19 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Iglino, 3 km from Kaltovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Kommunar, Republic of Bashkortostan
